  <title>Mobil Alanda NFC</title>
  <description />
  <content>&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span class="MsoIntenseReference"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings;"&gt;&amp;Oslash;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;NFC teknolojisi &amp;uuml;&amp;ccedil; farklı &amp;ccedil;alışma modunda veri iletişimini m&amp;uuml;mk&amp;uuml;n kılmaktadır: &lt;strong&gt;Okuyucu/Yazıcı&lt;/strong&gt; Modu (reader/writer mode), &amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Kart Em&amp;uuml;lasyon&lt;/strong&gt; Modu (card emulation mode) ve &lt;strong&gt;Birebir İletişim&lt;/strong&gt; Modu (p2p mode):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -36.0pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;OkuyOkuyucu/Yazıcı Modu ;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;Temassız sistem olarak ifade edilen bu sistemler &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;ISO 14443&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; grubuna dahil edilirler. ISO 14443 standardına g&amp;ouml;re cihaz ile kart okuyucu arasındaki uzaklık max. 10 cm olabilir. Ancak NFC de bu mesafe 2-4 cm arasındadır. Bu standardı kullanan &amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;nler &lt;strong&gt;RFID&lt;/strong&gt; olarak bilinen radyo dalgaları &amp;uuml;zerinden temassız olarak tanıma ve işlem yapan grubuna dahil edilir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img style="font-size: 10px;" src="/image.axd?picture=%2f2013%2f05%2fnfc2.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img style="font-size: 10px;" src="/image.axd?picture=%2f2013%2f05%2fnfc3.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;NFC &amp;ouml;zellikli mobil cihaz NFC etiketini okuyabilir, etikette depolanmış olan veriyi değiştirebilir, ya da etikete yeni bir veri yazabilir. Akıllı Poster uygulamaları, okuyucu/yazıcı modunu kullanan yaygın NFC uygulama &amp;ouml;rneklerinden biridir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -36.0pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;Kart &amp;nbsp;Kart Em&amp;uuml;lasyon Modu ;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -36.0pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;NFC cihaz i&amp;ccedil;erisinde bir&amp;ccedil;ok &amp;ouml;nemli bilgi barındırarak temassız bir akıllı kart gibi davranabilir. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;Y&amp;uuml;ksek frekansta (13.56 MHz) ve d&amp;uuml;ş&amp;uuml;k bant genişliğinde (en &amp;ccedil;ok 424Kbit/s) g&amp;uuml;venli bir aray&amp;uuml;z &amp;uuml;zerinden veri haberleşmesini sağlamaktadır.&lt;/span&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;NFC uyumlu mobil cihazın dokundurulmasıyla, cihaz &amp;uuml;zerindeki bilginin okuyucuya aktarımı ger&amp;ccedil;ekleşir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&lt;img style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10.399999618530273px; line-height: normal; text-indent: 0px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/image.axd?picture=%2f2013%2f05%2fnfc4.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -36.0pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -36.0pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;BirebBirebir İletişim Modu ( P-2-P ) &amp;nbsp;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -36.0pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;ISO/IEC 18092 ile standardize edilmiş olan birebir iletişim modu ise NFC uyumlu iki mobil cihaz arasında birebir bağlantı kurarak, veri değişimine olanak sağlar. NFC uyumlu mobil cihaz bir başka NFC uyumlu mobil cihaza yaklaştırıldığında veri transferi ger&amp;ccedil;ekleşir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -36.0pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;img style="font-size: 10px;" src="/image.axd?picture=%2f2013%2f05%2fnfc5.jpg" alt="" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Cambria; mso-fareast-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Cambria; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;1.&lt;span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;P2P Aktif - Pasif Mod&amp;nbsp; ;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 72.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo5;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;Bu modda, iki cihazdan biri olan P2P Initiator (Tetikleyici) manyetik bir alan oluşturur ve diğer cihaz olan P2P Target (Hedef) bu manyetik alandan etkilenerek dinleme konumuna ge&amp;ccedil;er.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 72.0pt; mso-add-space: auto;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;2.&lt;span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #984806; mso-themecolor: accent6; mso-themeshade: 128;"&gt;P2P Aktif - Aktif Mod &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 72.0pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo5;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"&gt;&amp;middot;&lt;span style="font-size: 7pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman';"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;Bu modda iki cihaz da manyetik alan oluşturur ve karşılıklı veri g&amp;ouml;nderilmesi yapılabilir. Oluşan manyetik alan i&amp;ccedil;erisinde simetrik olarak veri g&amp;ouml;nderimi ve alımı yapılabilir. Bu mod yavaştır, iletişim daha &amp;ccedil;ok zaman alır ve iki cihaz i&amp;ccedil;in de enerji t&amp;uuml;ketimi fazladır.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-left: 72.0pt; mso-add-space: auto;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings;"&gt;&amp;Oslash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;Mobil ekosistemde Nokia, &amp;nbsp;Apple, Google, HTC, BlackBerry, LG, SAMSUNG, Turkcell gibi bir &amp;ccedil;ok şirket NFC standardına sahip &amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;nler &amp;uuml;retmektedir.&amp;nbsp; Google Nexus S cihazı ile birlikte Android NFC uygulamalarını duyurmaya başladı.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Wingdings;"&gt;&amp;Oslash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Cambria, serif;"&gt;&amp;Uuml;reticiler tarafından son 2 yıla kadar kararlaştırılamayan g&amp;uuml;venlik elementinin cihazda mı yoksa sim kartta mı olacağı konusu hakkında sim kartta olacağı kararı alındı.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span class="MsoIntenseReference"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span class="MsoIntenseReference"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'Cambria','serif'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
